LORE SUCCESS!!! Koart is a village located within Cantrev Koart, an area claimed by the MacKorart clan. The MacKorats are a rich trading clan who benefit greatly from trade and investment in the neighbouring capital of Corwell. They are traditionally close allies of the MacDynnarts, who themselves own much of the cantrev that lies to the south of Corwell.
